name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Wingait FARMS, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Wingait FARMS, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 20th day of November, 1996, the Petitioner’s Petition for Writ of Supersedeas is GRANTED pending this Court’s final disposition of Commonwealth v. Wingait Farms, No. 81 Eastern District Appeal Docket 1995.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
